wiki.summary: “Mood Swings“ sees Pop Smoke reuniting with Bronx rapper Lil Tjay for a slow-moving track. The two take turns dropping references to their women and expensive items to boast about their lifestyle with fame. Pop and Tjay made this track the same night they made their October 2019 hit “War,“ a track which was featured on Pop’s 2020 mixtape, Meet The Woo 2. Read more on Last.fm.
